window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>DCI Lesley Clarke is settling into her new job in Dorset's Major Crimes Unit, and becoming accustomed to a slower pace of life.&nbsp;</p> <p>But then she's called in to solve the murder of a woman with links to Lesley's new girlfriend.</p> <p>Has Lesley made a grave error of judgement? Can she track down the killer, or does she already know her? And how will Lesley's new colleagues react when she tells them she's dating a suspect?</p> <p>The Clifftop Murders is the second installment in the gripping Dorset Crime series, in which rural Dorset is a whole lot darker than the holiday brochures would have you think.</p>"; 
